overview: Eight more episodes of the animated series following the adventures of the lovable sea sponge and his deep-sea friends in Bikini Bottom. Episodes are: 'To SquarePants or Not to SquarePants', 'Squid's Visit', 'Pineapple Fever', 'Chum Caverns', 'Boating Buddies', 'The Krabby Kronicle', 'The Slumber Party' and 'Grooming Gary'.
title: SPONGEBOB SQUAREPANTS - ROUND PANTS
